                            <h4>What does it mean to make a booking?</h4>
                            <p>
                                If you want to join a ride with someone from one place to the other on exact date, you can make a booking of his or her ride. After the driver accept
                                your request you can drive together to your destination.
                            </p>



                            <h4>How much does it cost to take a ride?</h4>

                            <p>Our application is fully without money. It means you will not be charged anything as well as no one will pay you for anything.</p>


                            <h4>How to make a booking?</h4>
                            <p>
                                You need to be logged in to book a ride. Go to the page with Rides where you can find the specific ride for you. After you have one, click on the
                                Details link in the end of the line where is the ride. You will see the page with all details and the driver. On the right side, there is a button for booking
                                the ride. After you click on it, you will see your list of bookings with the booking statuses. Now you have to wait until the driver accept or reject your request.
                                In case you have already booked the ride the button for booking it will not allow you to book it once again.
                            </p>


                            <h4>Where can I see my bookings?</h4>
                            <p>
                                To see your bookings you need to be logged in. Open your personal profile page and choose My bookings section. Here you can see the list of all your bookings with all their statuses.
                                Another faster way to see all of them is to click on Bookings button in the navigation bar on the top of the page next to Rides button.
                            </p>



                            <h4>Is it possible to cancel my booking?</h4>
                            <p>
                                You can always cancel the booking in case you cannot join the ride. You can do that on your own profile page in MyBookings section. There you can find the Cancel button next to the booking you wish to cancel. Make sure you are cancelling the right one.
                            </p>
                            <p>
                                Another way to do so is to open Bookings page on the top of the page, which will show you the list of your bookings. Here you can see the button Cancel
                                when your ride is accepted so that you can still cancel it anytime.
                            </p>
                            

                            <h4>Is it possible to delete my booking from the list?</h4>
                            <p>At the moment it is not possible.</p>

                                <h4>Is it possible to cancel the booking even after the driver has confirmed it?</h4>
                            <p>You can always cancel the booking if you cannot join the ride. To find more information how to cancel it, check the previous question Is it possible to cancel my booking?</p>





                            <h4>How do I know if my booking has been accepted by the driver?</h4>
                            <p>You can see it under the notification bell, Bookings page or under My bookings on your personal profile page. Each of these pages is showing the status of your bookings.</p>







                            <h4>How to contact a driver who accepted my booking?</h4>
                            <p>
                                To contact the driver, open the detailed page of the ride and there you can see the Area with Send me a message. This message is sent to the driver and when he or she wants to continue
                                in the conversation somehow, you can find more messages under message picture on the top of the page. To find out more about Message, check the Messages section in questions for everyone using the App.
