                                    <h4>What can others see about me?</h4>
                                    <p>Other people will see your First name, last name, gender as well as your avatar and introduction inserted in About me area.</p>



                                    <h4>How to edit my information?</h4>
                                    <p>
                                        To edit your personal information, open the profile page by clicking up on the right side of the page on your name. Of course to see this button you need to be logged in.You will be
                                        redirected to your personal profile page with your information. You can add your gender and introduction here or change your Name and Surname in case you did a typo while registering.
                                        When you are finished, do not forget to Save your changes with the button under the About Me area.
                                    </p>



                                    <h4>How to delete my account?</h4>
                                    <p>
                                        To delete your account you have to be logged in. Open your personal profile page and choose Delete Account option on your left side.
                                        The question if you are really sure you want to do so appears. So if you are really sure, click on Delete button and you will be redirected to the page, where you have to confirm the deleting procedure
                                        with your current password. After you Confirm the password you will be logged out of your account and it will not be possible to log in again with previous information.
